node.text:
Good news, I’m going on a book tour with @boazfrankel ✨📚✨ If you live in Austin, Boston, NYC, Minneapolis, Detroit, San Francisco, Portland Oregon, or Pittsburgh I’d love if you came and let me draw in your book! I also have stories and things to read and we have prizes to give you, and I’d love to meet you.

If you live in another city anywhere in the world please comment and tell me where, so we can try to go there next! (@workmanpub are you listening?) Mark your calendars and go to brookeandboaz.com/tour for more info. 
See you soon, weirdos.
